overview:
Maps.com is a leading provider of mapping products and solutions to business, education and consumer markets. Founded in 1991 as Magellan Geographix, Maps.com is privately held with four primary business divisions.

As industry leaders in the online commerce marketplace, Maps.com has earned status of The Largest Online US Map Store (Alexa ranking June 2011) with 10,000 products available, including Wall Maps, Globes, Atlases, Online Mapping Tools and much more.

Our online commerce is strengthened by an affiliate network of over 3,000 web publishers, further extending Maps.com to websites worldwide. Adding to the retail emphasis is our useful and fun contentâ€”driving directions, an online world atlas, and even interactive map games. As a premiere online destination, Maps.com continually provides products and information to millions of visitors.
